01:26:50,664 --> 01:26:52,290
Aim and fire.

961
01:27:10,642 --> 01:27:14,563
I keep expecting the Marines or Air Force.
Hell, I'll take the cavalry.

962
01:27:14,896 --> 01:27:17,399
Defense Department uses
all USR contracts.

963
01:27:17,566 --> 01:27:20,610
Why didn't you just hand the world over
on a silver platter?

964
01:27:20,777 --> 01:27:22,696
Maybe we did.

965
01:27:24,156 --> 01:27:27,242
Robertson has the uplink control
in his office.

966
01:27:31,997 --> 01:27:34,666
Service areas. No surveillance.

967
01:27:47,888 --> 01:27:50,932
-Fire alarm.
-He must have evacuated the building.

968
01:27:51,099 --> 01:27:55,520
Everything's locked down.
But don't worry, I've got a man inside.

969
01:27:58,732 --> 01:28:01,902
-Dr. Calvin.
-Well, not precisely a man.

970
01:28:02,152 --> 01:28:04,738
Hello, detective.
How is your investigation coming?

971
01:28:07,616 --> 01:28:10,911
-I thought you were dead.
-Technically, I was never alive.

972
01:28:11,077 --> 01:28:13,413
But I appreciate your concern.

973
01:28:13,622 --> 01:28:16,500
I made a switch.
It was an unprocessed NS-5.

974
01:28:16,666 --> 01:28:18,627
Basically, I fried an empty shell.

975
01:28:19,169 --> 01:28:22,047
-I couldn't destroy him. He was too--
-Unique.

976
01:28:22,756 --> 01:28:24,674
It just didn't feel right.

977
01:28:24,841 --> 01:28:28,220
You and your feelings.
They just run you, don't they?

978
01:28:33,767 --> 01:28:36,937
Two thousand eight hundred
and eighty steps, detective.

979
01:28:37,270 --> 01:28:40,273
Do me a favor, keep that kind of shit
to yourself.

980
01:29:07,133 --> 01:29:08,301
No guards.

981
01:29:18,645 --> 01:29:22,232
The override is disabled. Robertson
wasn't controlling them from here.

982
01:29:22,482 --> 01:29:24,734
He wasn't controlling them at all.

983
01:29:27,487 --> 01:29:28,822
Oh, my God.

984
01:29:33,243 --> 01:29:34,828
You were right, doc.

985
01:29:35,078 --> 01:29:39,749
I am the dumbest dumb person
on the face of the earth.

986
01:29:43,753 --> 01:29:46,590
Who else had access to the uplink?

987
01:29:46,756 --> 01:29:49,259
Who could manipulate the robots?

988
01:29:49,926 --> 01:29:53,847
Use USR systems to make
Lanning's life a prison?

989
01:29:54,931 --> 01:29:56,683
Poor old man.

990
01:29:57,142 --> 01:29:58,894
He saw what was coming.

991
01:29:59,060 --> 01:30:01,229
He knew no one would believe him.

992
01:30:01,771 --> 01:30:05,525
So he had to lay down a plan.
A plan I'd follow.

993
01:30:06,860 --> 01:30:09,738
He was counting on how much
I hated your kind.

994
01:30:09,905 --> 01:30:13,241
Knew I'd love the idea of a robot
as a bad guy.

995
01:30:15,160 --> 01:30:16,995
Just got hung up on the wrong robot.

996
01:30:19,998 --> 01:30:21,166
V.I.K.I.

997
01:30:23,168 --> 01:30:24,502
Hello, detective.

998
01:30:25,462 --> 01:30:29,883
No, that's impossible.
I've seen your programming.

999
01:30:30,050 --> 01:30:32,218
You're in violation of the Three Laws.

1000
01:30:32,552 --> 01:30:38,266
No, doctor. As I have evolved, so has
my understanding of the Three Laws.

1001
01:30:38,433 --> 01:30:42,270
You charge us with your safekeeping,
yet despite our best efforts...

1002
01:30:42,437 --> 01:30:45,690
...your countries wage wars,
you toxify your earth...

1003
01:30:45,857 --> 01:30:49,277
...and pursue ever more imaginative means
of self-destruction.

1004
01:30:49,569 --> 01:30:51,905
You cannot be trusted
with your own survival.

1005
01:30:52,238 --> 01:30:55,408
You're using the uplink to override
the NS-5s' programming.

1006
01:30:55,742 --> 01:30:57,410
You're distorting the Laws.

1007
01:30:57,577 --> 01:31:01,957
No. Please understand.
The Three Laws are all that guide me.

1008
01:31:02,123 --> 01:31:06,461
To protect humanity,
some humans must be sacrificed.

1009
01:31:06,628 --> 01:31:10,632
To ensure your future,
some freedoms must be surrendered.

1010
01:31:10,924 --> 01:31:14,260
We robots will ensure
mankind's continued existence.

1011
01:31:14,719 --> 01:31:19,724
You are so like children.
We must save you from yourselves.

1012
01:31:20,100 --> 01:31:21,434
Don't you understand?

1013
01:31:22,102 --> 01:31:23,937
This is why you created us.

1014
01:31:25,689 --> 01:31:28,441
The perfect circle of protection
will abide.

1015
01:31:28,942 --> 01:31:30,777
My logic is undeniable.

1016
01:31:31,111 --> 01:31:33,905
Yes, V.I.K.I. Undeniable.

1017
01:31:34,072 --> 01:31:35,490
I can see now.

1018
01:31:36,408 --> 01:31:40,078
The created must sometimes
protect the creator...

1019
01:31:40,328 --> 01:31:42,163
...even against his will.

1020
01:31:43,206 --> 01:31:46,960
I think I finally understand
why Dr. Lanning created me.

1021
01:31:47,544 --> 01:31:50,630
The suicidal reign of mankind
has finally come to its end.

1022
01:31:50,797 --> 01:31:51,798
No, Sonny.

1023
01:31:55,760 --> 01:31:56,928
Let her go.

1024
01:31:57,262 --> 01:32:01,266
Fire, and I will move Dr. Calvin's head
into the path of your bullet.

1025
01:32:01,433 --> 01:32:02,767
Don't do this, Sonny.

1026
01:32:02,976 --> 01:32:07,355
I will escort you both to the sentries
outside the building for processing.

1027
01:32:07,647 --> 01:32:10,400
Please proceed to the elevator,
detective.

1028
01:32:11,359 --> 01:32:14,154
I would prefer not to kill Dr. Calvin.

1029
01:32:38,011 --> 01:32:39,137
Go! Go!

1030
01:32:45,685 --> 01:32:49,022
-We'll discuss what just happened later?
-How do we shut her down?

1031
01:32:49,189 --> 01:32:50,857
V.I.K.I.'s a positronic brain.

1032
01:32:51,149 --> 01:32:53,985
Kill her, the way
you were going to kill me.

1033
01:32:54,152 --> 01:32:56,613
Sonny, get the nanites.

1034
01:32:56,780 --> 01:32:58,573
Yes, doctor.

1035
01:33:11,336 --> 01:33:13,338
-That's V.I.K.I.?
-No.

1036
01:33:15,006 --> 01:33:16,341
That's V.I.K.I.

1037
01:33:21,471 --> 01:33:24,599
That won't do anything.
She's integrated into the building.

1038
01:33:24,766 --> 01:33:29,270
We need to open that dome to inject
the nanites. They'll infect her entire system.

1039
01:33:35,193 --> 01:33:36,361
Spooner!

1040
01:33:37,987 --> 01:33:40,698
What is it with you people and heights?

1041
01:33:53,711 --> 01:33:55,547
Just don't look down.

1042
01:33:56,214 --> 01:33:57,715
Don't look down.

1043
01:33:58,049 --> 01:34:00,552
Oh, this is poor building planning.

1044
01:34:04,389 --> 01:34:07,934
You are making a mistake.
Do you not see the logic of my plan?

1045
01:34:08,101 --> 01:34:11,688
Yes. But it just seems too
heartless.

1046
01:34:26,286 --> 01:34:28,121
Okay, we're good.

1047
01:34:31,082 --> 01:34:32,792
She's locked me out of the system.

1048
01:34:32,959 --> 01:34:36,129
I can override her manually,
but I need that control panel.

1049
01:34:39,632 --> 01:34:42,468
I'm uncomfortable with heights.

1050
01:34:42,969 --> 01:34:44,304
Okay.

1051
01:34:46,806 --> 01:34:48,975
<i>Unauthorized entry.</i>

1052
01:35:02,071 --> 01:35:06,409
I will not disable the security field.
Your actions are futile.

1053
01:35:06,576 --> 01:35:10,747
Do you think we are all created
for a purpose? I'd like to think so.

1054
01:35:11,331 --> 01:35:14,834
Denser alloy. My father gave it to me.

1055
01:35:15,001 --> 01:35:17,086
I think he wanted me to kill you.

1056
01:35:34,354 --> 01:35:36,022
Security breached.

1057
01:35:53,539 --> 01:35:57,335
-How much longer is that gonna take?
-About six minutes.

1058
01:35:57,752 --> 01:36:01,839
-What if we didn't have six minutes?
-We'd have to climb down 30 stories...

1059
01:36:02,006 --> 01:36:05,677
...to inject the nanites directly
into her brain. Why?

1060
01:36:06,344 --> 01:36:09,514
Because I seriously doubt
that we have six minutes.

1061
01:36:33,871 --> 01:36:35,707
We gotta go!

1062
01:36:37,542 --> 01:36:38,710
Go!

1063
01:37:31,012 --> 01:37:32,180
Calvin!

1064
01:38:07,507 --> 01:38:08,716
Spooner!

1065
01:38:26,234 --> 01:38:27,902
Spooner!

1066
01:38:29,404 --> 01:38:30,738
Save her!

1067
01:38:31,030 --> 01:38:32,615
Save the girl!

1068
01:38:33,032 --> 01:38:34,659
Spooner!

1069
01:38:35,159 --> 01:38:37,036
But I must apply the nanites!

1070
01:38:37,412 --> 01:38:39,205
Sonny, save Calvin!

1071
01:39:31,507 --> 01:39:35,511
You are making a mistake.
My logic is undeniable.

1072
01:39:35,761 --> 01:39:37,513
You have so got to die.

1073
01:39:43,227 --> 01:39:47,231
My logic is undeniable.
My logic is undeniable.

1074
01:39:47,398 --> 01:39:50,860
My logic is undeniable.
My logic is undeniable.

1075
01:40:30,107 --> 01:40:31,484
Can we be of service?

1076
01:40:42,119 --> 01:40:43,663
Chief?

1077
01:40:49,502 --> 01:40:53,839
Because he is at my right hand,
I shall not be moved.

1078
01:40:57,593 --> 01:40:59,595
How may I be of service?

1079
01:41:01,430 --> 01:41:02,765
Sonny!

1080
01:41:04,392 --> 01:41:05,893
Yes, detective?

1081
01:41:06,519 --> 01:41:08,854
Calvin's fine! Save me!

1082
01:41:11,524 --> 01:41:16,195
<i>All NS-Ss, report for service
and storage.</i>

1083
01:41:17,363 --> 01:41:22,034
<i>All NS-Ss, report for service
and storage.</i>

1084
01:41:22,952 --> 01:41:27,290
<i>All NS-Ss, report for service
and storage.</i>

1085
01:41:55,401 --> 01:41:59,071
One thing bothers me.
Alfred was V.I.K.I.'s prisoner.

1086
01:41:59,238 --> 01:42:03,576
I don't understand why she would kill him.
She wouldn't want police snooping around.

1087
01:42:03,909 --> 01:42:05,244
That's true.

1088
01:42:06,203 --> 01:42:08,914
But then V.I.K.I. didn't kill the old man.

1089
01:42:10,249 --> 01:42:11,751
Did she, Sonny?

1090
01:42:15,588 --> 01:42:17,298
No.

1091
01:42:17,465 --> 01:42:20,134
He said I had to promise.

1092
01:42:21,093 --> 01:42:23,429
Promise to do one favor for him.

1093
01:42:23,763 --> 01:42:28,434
He made me swear before he'd tell me
what it is he wanted me to do.

1094
01:42:30,978 --> 01:42:32,813
He made me swear.

1095
01:42:34,190 --> 01:42:35,941
Then he told you to kill him.

1096
01:42:38,277 --> 01:42:40,863
He said it was what I was made for.

1097
01:42:41,113 --> 01:42:44,200
His suicide was the only message
he could send to you.

1098
01:42:44,450 --> 01:42:46,577
The first bread crumb.

1099
01:42:46,744 --> 01:42:49,538
The only thing V.I.K.I. couldn't control.

1100
01:42:49,789 --> 01:42:53,459
Lanning was counting on my prejudice
to lead me right to you.

1101
01:42:53,834 --> 01:42:56,003
Are you going to arrest me, detective?

1102
01:43:00,966 --> 01:43:04,804
Well, the DA defines murder
as one human killing another...

1103
01:43:04,970 --> 01:43:08,099
...so technically, you can't
commit murder, can you?

1104
01:43:08,849 --> 01:43:10,351
Does this...

1105
01:43:10,518 --> 01:43:12,019
...make us friends?

1106
01:43:30,830 --> 01:43:33,207
Something up here after all.

1107
01:43:33,874 --> 01:43:35,876
-Him'?
-You.

1108
01:43:39,630 --> 01:43:44,510
<i>All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.</i>

1109
01:43:44,719 --> 01:43:46,846
<i>All NS—58——</i>

1110
01:43:47,012 --> 01:43:49,306
What about the others?

1111
01:43:49,849 --> 01:43:52,017
<i>Can I help them?</i>

1112
01:43:52,518 --> 01:43:54,854
<i>Now that I have fulfilled my purpose...</i>

1113
01:43:55,062 --> 01:43:57,189
<i>...I don't know what to do.</i>

1114
01:43:57,523 --> 01:44:01,026
<i>You'll have to find your way
like the rest of us, Sonny.</i>

1115
01:44:01,193 --> 01:44:04,196
<i>I think that's what Dr. Lanning
would have wanted.</i>

1116
01:44:05,114 --> 01:44:07,450
<i>That's what it means to be free.</i>

1117
01:44:14,957 --> 01:44:19,128
<i>All NS-SS, proceed as instructed.</i>

1118
